{
  "stem": "13063.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First of all, the ghetto was surrounded by-- by the German military, by SS with machine guns, with-- with posts, with, you know, like-- like regular siege, a wartime siege of the ghetto, so nobody should-- and they rounded up everybody.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everybody.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, of course.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There-- there was a whole army, detachments of German soldiers coming, SS coming and-- and-- and rounding up people and pushing them towards the plaza, to the-- to-- towards the square, the big square, where-- where everybody was-- was gathered there.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whoever hid was shot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I heard many shots.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People who were hiding were taken out and shot right on the spot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So when my-- yeah, so we went all with the transport.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were already on the way to the rail-- the railroad station, or railroad gathering place.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With my father and my mother and my sister.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All of a sudden, I saw a German on the side gathering a small group of the people where I was working for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, there was an outpost that I was working, the-- the-- the-- it was called Sonderdienst, S-O-N-D-E-R-D-I-N-S-T, Sonderdienst.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In 1942, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was detached with my father to work for that particular German outpost, or place of work.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think destiny.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was destiny.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were just commanded to go there, and we worked there day by day, every day.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] because while we were walking, I saw the German, and I felt like an angel pushed me towards that German.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the-- the German was the-- the overseer of our work detachment in Sonderdienst.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Thiele.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His name was Thiele, T-H-I-E-L-E.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was his name.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
